{"tid":1407321,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"罷交稅後果， 癱瘓政府?","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:17:53.000Z","uid":298372,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b01fffe19e1743d4ba8d4e98b455a616cb18bab","tid":1407321,"uid":298372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:11:15.000Z","msg":"見住個政府不聽民意，警察欺人太甚暴力鎮壓，我決定撕毀報稅表。<br />\n<br />\n假設一人一罷交，稅局逐個人追會增加成本同埋時間上處理唔切，法院要逐個人告的話，告排得期黎政府已經無錢再運作，而市民解釋遲遲未收到報稅表。<br />\n<br />\n想問大家有無野miss到?"},{"pid":"05115fba6418883b647d0877e28bf8c9da9346ca","tid":1407321,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:01:12.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n全民罷稅 正式啟動<br />\n<br />\n一個人罷稅 = 逃稅<br />\n五十萬人罷稅率 = 對政府施壓"},{"pid":"eef6a8d82f814ccc5f47b3c9da1c656f329accbb","tid":1407321,"uid":127013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:04:36.000Z","msg":"政府會自動在户口扣，連罰款"},{"pid":"5f76d541e67475ce9579371c41bb3693b19ce21e","tid":1407321,"uid":298372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef6a8d82f814ccc5f47b3c9da1c656f329accbb","tid":1407321,"uid":127013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:04:36.000Z","msg":"政府會自動在户口扣，連罰款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:17:53.000Z","msg":"本身無連接戶口"}]}